==English==
=== Noun phrase ===
'''a [[cold]] [[day]] in [[hell]]'''

# ''Slang'' An event that will never happen.
#:''Yea, that will happen if it is '''a cold day in hell'''.''

====Translations====
*Dutch: [[met Sint Juttemis]]
*German: wenn die Hölle zufriert
*Hungarian: [[majd ha piros hó esik]] (when red snowflakes is snowing), [[majd ha cigánygyerekek potyognak az égből]] (when gipsy childs are streaming from the sky), [[majd ha a pokol befagy]] (when hell freezes over)

*French: [[quand les poules auront des dents]] (When hens will have teeth), [[la semaine des quatre jeudis]] (on the week with four thursdays)

